metadata.name: HanziNFT #1
metadata.description: The Hanzi NFT collection reflects the beauty in Chinese characters (汉字 Hanzi) and the essence of eastern philosophy. The collection contains NFTs presenting Hanzi together with a bilingual and philosophical motto in customized or AI-generated designs. We gift each Hanzi NFT to the pioneers who contribute to intellectual conversations of profound insights and practical impacts at SciEcon.
